Zm_zerbes_corruption

Map by: Zerberus

I made this Map for a little Contest in my Community against 4 other Mappers. The job was to made a zm_ map in Prison style. 
There are fewer hiding spots then in other maps, so the humans must work together to survive. I think the map would be a better cs_map xD.

Features:
- 60 Spawnpoints
- 1 micro secret (xD)
- 1 medium secret
- a lot of differnt rooms
- no ultimate camper spot (like ventilation shaft)


So... I hope you enjoy my work and maybe some of you can help me to fix some bugs, which I can't fix (lol).
like the lightbug in the "registration room"

Pls rate & subscribe


- Zerberus -
